  "description": "Write a SQL query using window functions to produce the requested analytical output.\n\n### Tables\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE accounts (\n  account_id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,\n  owner_name TEXT NOT NULL,\n  segment TEXT NOT NULL\n);\n\nCREATE TABLE transactions (\n  txn_id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,\n  account_id INTEGER NOT NULL,\n  txn_date TEXT NOT NULL,\n  amount INTEGER NOT NULL,\n  txn_type TEXT NOT NULL\n);\n```\n\n### Task\nAssign debit transactions to quartiles using amount DESC and NTILE(4)-style buckets.\n\n### Return Columns\n- `txn_id`\n- `amount`\n- `quartile`\n\n### Ordering\nSort by `amount` DESC, then `txn_id` ASC.\n\n### Notes\n- Use SQLite syntax.\n- Write your answer in `solution.sql`.\n- Do not hardcode output rows; query from tables.\n- Internal hidden tests run against additional seed data.",
